title: Combine preview with Bucky Brooks
itunes:title: Combine preview with Bucky Brooks
description:
A room filled with some heroes – Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler  – discuss the latest NFL news including Peyton Manning returning for the 2015 season and the Rams sticking with Sam Bradford. Plus, Bucky Brooks joins the show to discuss what he’s looking for from players at the NFL Combine.
